        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You create a cloud of putrid mist in the area. The cloud functions as <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Obscuring Mist]{Obscuring Mist}</em> except it sickens creatures that end their turns within the cloud. (The @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Concealed]{Concealed} condition is not a poison effect.)</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Sickened]{Sickened 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Sickened]{Sickened 1} and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Slowed]{Slowed 1} while in the cloud.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Sickened]{Sickened 2} and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Slowed]{Slowed 1} until it leaves the cloud.</p>"
